# Keep the Docker build context small and deterministic. Applies to builds whose
# context is the repository root (e.g. samples/Centralized.Sample/Dockerfile).
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
.git/
.github/
**/*.user
**/TestResults/
artifacts/
# Local SQLite quickstart leftovers.
**/featly*.db
**/featly*.db-shm
**/featly*.db-wal
